    <br>
    what about using "a la" log4c verbosity names ?<br>
    <a class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/log4c/">http://sourceforge.net/projects/log4c/</a><br>
    <br>
    static const char* const priorities[] = {<br>
        "FATAL",<br>
        "ALERT",<br>
        "CRIT",<br>
        "ERROR",<br>
        "WARN",<br>
        "NOTICE",<br>
        "INFO",<br>
        "DEBUG",<br>
        "TRACE",<br>
        "NOTSET",<br>
